turnkey-appengine-python-12.1 (1) turnkey; urgency=low

  * AppEngine Python:

    - Upgraded to latest version.
    - Replaced overlayed template-django with inline downloads and configuration.
    - Replaced offline docs with online links (no longer available).
    - Deny browsing to google_appengine apps sourcecode (security).

    - Added mercurial (required for template-django dep download).
    - Added ipython (convenience).

  * Upstream source component versions:

    google_appengine            1.7.5

